    "## 8. Pressure Calculation\n",
    "\n",
    "The pressure of a LJ fluid via the virial equation:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$P = \\rho k_B T + \\frac{1}{3V} \\left\\langle \\sum_{i<j} r_{ij} F_{ij} \\right\\rangle$$\n",
    "\n",
    "where the first term is the ideal gas contribution and the second is the virial correction."
   ]
