    "MSD $\\langle \\Delta r^2(t) \\rangle$ characterizes particle diffusion:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$MSD(t) = \\langle |r(t) - r(0)|^2 \\rangle$$\n",
    "\n",
    "In the diffusive regime: $MSD(t) = 6Dt$ where $D$ is the diffusion coefficient."
