    "\n",
    "This notebook demonstrates all the core building blocks for the simulation engine:\n",
    "\n",
    "| Component | What it does | Key insight |\n",
    "|-----------|-------------|-------------|\n",
    "| LJ Potential | Pairwise interactions | $r_{min} = 2^{1/6}σ$ |\n",
    "| PBC | Bulk matter simulation | Minimum image convention |\n",
    "| NVE (Velocity-Verlet) | Energy-conserving integration | $\\Delta E < 0.01\\%$ for $\\Delta t = 0.002$ |\n",
    "| Langevin | Friction + noise thermostat | Fluctuation-dissipation theorem |\n",
    "| Andersen | Stochastic collision thermostat | Correct ensemble, breaks momentum |\n",
    "| RDF | Structure factor | $g(r) \\to 1$ for ideal gas |\n",
    "| Pressure | Virial equation | $P = \\rho kT + \\text{virial}/3V$ |\n",
    "| MSD | Diffusion measurement | Linear in time for diffusive regime |\n",
